00:34:54.930 --> 00:35:02.850
It requires making sure that
when women talk or men talk,

00:35:02.850 --> 00:35:07.610
your child learns
how not to interrupt.

00:35:07.610 --> 00:35:15.640
It means, teaching him that
listening to people's ideas,

00:35:15.640 --> 00:35:20.460
requiring letting them
talk those ideas out.

00:35:20.460 --> 00:35:25.610
It requires teaching him
by example and otherwise

00:35:25.610 --> 00:35:29.010
that women do powerful things.

00:35:29.010 --> 00:35:31.510
And you can show him a
Supreme Court with three women.

00:35:31.510 --> 00:35:43.120
