00:35:53.030 --> 00:36:02.110
[ Applause ]

00:36:02.110 --> 00:36:05.570
It's about my friend
and I'm privileged

00:36:05.570 --> 00:36:08.430
to call her my friend,
but she was an advocate

00:36:08.430 --> 00:36:10.980
for women's rights.

00:36:10.980 --> 00:36:16.420
And I don't know that any other
movie I have ever seen might

00:36:16.420 --> 00:36:21.510
teach your son why equality
of women is so important.

00:36:21.510 --> 00:36:29.750
[ Applause ]

00:36:29.750 --> 00:36:31.050
Don't give up on him.

00:36:31.050 --> 00:36:32.350
They all grow up.

