&gt;&gt; CARLA HAYDEN: Justice.

00:51:39.840 --> 00:51:41.140
&gt;&gt; JUSTICE SONIA SOTOMAYOR: Yes?

00:51:41.140 --> 00:51:44.030
&gt;&gt; CARLA HAYDEN: I know that
