&gt;&gt; CARLA HAYDEN: I know you
want to talk and shake hands

00:51:51.690 --> 00:51:54.330
and come back this way.

00:51:54.330 --> 00:51:59.140
Would you mind if I read a
little bit from the last part

00:51:59.140 --> 00:52:00.440
of your book as you come.

00:52:00.440 --> 00:52:01.740
&gt;&gt; JUSTICE SONIA SOTOMAYOR: I'm
going to come up, I promise you.

00:52:01.740 --> 00:52:03.040
&gt;&gt; CARLA HAYDEN: You come on up.

00:52:03.040 --> 00:52:05.340
&gt;&gt; JUSTICE SONIA
SOTOMAYOR: I'll get around.

00:52:11.120 --> 00:52:13.270
How you guys up there?

